  "teamManagement.pack4": "Agraw n 4",
  "infosPack3": "Arnu-d 1 ɣer 3 n iɛeggalen ɣer wegraw n tḥanuţ-ik/im, i wakken ad tezmireḍ ad as-n-tefkeḍ i yal yiwen axeddim ara yexdem s daxel n Cegget. Tzemreḍ ad textireḍ i yal aɛeggal axeddim i tevɣiḍ ad yexdem. \n Iɛeggalen zemren ad walin yiwen seg igdilen (écrans) ara sen-t-ǧǧeḍ ad walin. Zemren ad walin: \n • Agdil (écran) Taḥanuţ-iw: zemren ad rren isufar ijdiden, ad ksen isufar, ad vedlen isallen ɣef usafar neɣ teswiṛa-ines. \n • Agdil (écran) n Teɣwalt (Ma Com'): ma tserḥeḍ i uɛeggal ad yesexdem agdil-agi, ad yizmir ad yerr teswiṛat ɣef tḥanuţ-ik/im d wayen i yellan akk deg-s i wakken ad izmiren medden ad ẓren ayen i yellan ɣeṛ-k/m. \n • Agdil (écran) n Isawaḍen (Commandes): Ma tserḥeḍ i uɛeggal ad yesexdem agdil-agi, ad yizmir ad iẓẓer akk isawaḍen ara d-yawḍen akken ad yizmir ad ten-id-iheggi. Ad yizmir ad iẓẓer anwa asafar d wacḥal i ilaqen ad tid iheggi. \n Ihi ma yella tevɣiḍ ad testaɛfuḍ iman-ik/im s uɛemmaṛ n isalen ɣef isufar, neɣ si tririt n teswiṛat, neɣ n uheggi n isufar n isawaen, ihi Premium-agi yeţwaxdam i keč/kem. I 3600 DZD kan i useggas ad tizmireḍ ad tesɛuḍ.",
  "infosPack4": "I 4800 DZD kan i useggas, ad tizmireḍ ad tesɛuḍ akk ayen i yellan di Agraw n 3, u ad rnuḍ yiwen n uɛeggal ara yizmiren ad isexdem: \n • Agdil (écran) n Tɛezzult: akka ad yizmir ad iwali ayen akk ara d-ikecmen seg isawaḍen. Ad iwali ssuma n yal asafar, ssuma n yal asaweḍ. U ma yella ur telliḍ ara di tḥanuţ ad yeṭṭef idrimen ara d-ikecmen.",
  "textePresentationPremium": "Tevɣiḍ ad tesfaydiḍ di Cegget akken iy laq? Premium agi yeţwaxdam i keč/kem!!",
  "weWillContactYouForPayment": "Ad ak/am-d nessiwel i wakken ad nehdeṛ ɣef lexlaṣ",
